getSynonyms

Collection<String> getSynonyms()
Provides a list of synonyms commonly used to describe the database of this identifier. For example Enzyme Nomenclature is more frequently referred to as EC. The synonyms are specified in the IdentifierDescription.properites file. If no synonyms are present an empty collection is returned
